      "text": "Which of the following types of ocular injuries can result from blunt trauma to the eye? 1) 2) 3) 4)",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "A",
          "text": "2 and 4",
          "correct": false
        },
        {
          "label": "B",
          "text": "1 and 2",
          "correct": false
        },
        {
          "label": "C",
          "text": "3 and 1",
          "correct": false
        },
        {
          "label": "D",
          "text": "All of the Above",
          "correct": true
        }
      ],
      "correct_answer": "D. All of the Above",
